19:26.077 --> 19:27.209
I do.
[ Exhales sharply ]

19:27.253 --> 19:28.384
[ Snorts ]

19:28.428 --> 19:29.777
No, no, don't move.
Ow.

19:29.820 --> 19:32.171
Okay. What made you
change your mind?

19:32.301 --> 19:33.346
I just don't think

19:33.389 --> 19:35.826
it's a decision I can make
with my mind.

19:37.393 --> 19:38.351
I'm scared.

19:38.394 --> 19:40.222
[ Chuckles ]
I'm scared, too.

19:40.266 --> 19:41.441
[ Both chuckling ]

19:41.484 --> 19:43.225
Do -- Do we -- Do we needto start right now?

19:43.269 --> 19:44.226
[ Chuckles ]

19:44.270 --> 19:46.315
Let's just...

19:46.446 --> 19:49.013
Let's just cuddle.
Okay.

19:49.057 --> 19:50.276
[ Sighs ]

19:50.319 --> 19:53.192
I want to be, like,
old parents, you know?

19:53.322 --> 19:54.454
Oh, yeah, yeah.

19:54.497 --> 19:56.412
Yeah, I'd like to belike Clint Eastwood

19:56.543 --> 19:58.066
with a brand-new baby.

19:58.109 --> 19:59.807
[ Laughs ] Yeah.
[ Sniffles ]

19:59.850 --> 20:02.288
You know, when I take the babyto the grocery store

20:02.331 --> 20:04.464
and ask where the diapers are,I want the person to say,

20:04.507 --> 20:05.378
"For which one of you?"

20:05.421 --> 20:07.945
[ Laughs ]

20:11.558 --> 20:13.124
Alright.
Mm, smokin' hot.

20:13.168 --> 20:14.604
Set it on fire, baby.

20:14.648 --> 20:16.127
-[ Laughs ] Take one.
-[ Chuckles ]

20:17.564 --> 20:18.347
I got a pretty good hand.

20:18.478 --> 20:19.957
I think I can do this
on my own.

20:21.959 --> 20:23.439
♪♪

20:23.570 --> 20:26.834
♪♪

20:26.877 --> 20:33.057
♪♪

20:33.101 --> 20:34.624
Pass.

20:34.668 --> 20:38.019
Okay, Kay has
one card left.

20:38.149 --> 20:40.717
If it's the Jack of Hearts,
she and Beau win.

20:40.761 --> 20:42.458
Who are you
talking to, honey?

20:42.589 --> 20:43.633
♪♪

20:43.677 --> 20:47.246
[ Imitating wood chipper
buzzing ]

20:47.376 --> 20:48.290
[ Constance and Rudy laugh ]

20:48.334 --> 20:50.118
Beau: Oh, my God.

20:50.161 --> 20:53.295
You have the Jack of Hearts.

20:53.339 --> 20:55.906
-[ Laughing ]
-[ Groaning ] No, no...

20:55.950 --> 20:57.952
-[ Laughter continues ]-Looks like your wood chipper's

20:57.995 --> 21:00.476
all jammed up, Rudy!

21:00.520 --> 21:02.130
[ Laughs ] I won!

21:02.173 --> 21:05.089
I paid attention to my wife,
and I won!

21:05.133 --> 21:07.135
-[ Laughs ]
-Whoo!

21:07.178 --> 21:08.571
Suck on that!

21:08.615 --> 21:10.486
[ All gasp ]

21:10.530 --> 21:12.488
Oh, boy, oh, boy,
this could be it.

21:12.619 --> 21:14.316
I could spin completely
out of control.

21:16.144 --> 21:18.929
No, I've got a handle on it.
We're good.
